name: First Love
description:
Remember how it felt? When, you saw her for the first time? Those beautiful eyes, butterflies...there's something about her when at some random moments when our eyes meet, sparks fly, heartbeats, she leans, I lean...magic happens as we kiss. I still remember how it feels. Just like the first time. Magical, wonderful, like first love 

Made in Procreate
Based on a true story of love and letting go.
